GLADNEY v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 63,

September Term, 1962.]

Decided February 15, 1963.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott, Horney, Marbury and Sybert, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons given by Judge Manley for denying relief below, this application for leave to appeal is hereby denied.
